	  with matrices

	* src/gnome-genius.c: flush after error display

Wed Oct 09 12:32:45 2002  George Lebl <jirka@5z.com>

	* src/gnome-genius.c, src/inter.c, src/Makefile.am,
	  src/genius-readline-helper.c:  Build the readline helper and
